{"tid":33705,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[EDM]電音及製作交流","createTime":"2016-12-11T03:57:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T12:44:02.000Z","uid":63158,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b865465a8564f6823195f27944823a029c0a93c0","tid":33705,"uid":63158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T03:57:46.000Z","msg":"做咗CD ROM好耐，特此發文慶祝連登啟業！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我聽開Avicii, Alesso, Flume, Martin Garrix, Marshmello, Galantis, Porter Robinson, Madeon, Oliver Heldens, KSHMR, Zedd 等等大路製作人。<br />\n<br />\n比較小眾嘅有<span style=\"color: gold;\">Grey, Kap Slap, Justin Caruso.</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (高度推薦)<br />\n<br />\n喜愛類型: Big Room, Dubstep, Melodic Progressive House, Future House, Futurebass, Melbourne Bounce, Chill.<br />\n<br />\n=====================================<br />\n<br />\nMusic Production方面，玩咗幾年，未有起色，不過基本功尚足。<br />\n用過Ableton Live, 依家係FL Studio忠粉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSamples儲埋成107GB, 不過最常用嘅有12.7GB. KSHMR Sounds, Cymatics, Vengeance House, 都係高質samples.<br />\n<br />\nSynth/Sound Plugin: Sylenth1, Massive, Serum, Spire, Addictive Keys, Kontakt 5.<br />\n<br />\nFX Plugin: Fabfilters, Valhalla DSP, Dimension Expander, OTT, Camel Crusher. Waves Complete Bundle. <br />\n<br />\n以上所提及嘅，夠你做Avicii, Martin Garrix嗰啲架啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n=====================================<br />\n<br />\nEssential Knowledge:<br />\nSound Design, Layering, Mixing(EQ, Pan), Automation, Compression, Arrangement.<br />\n<br />\n呢啲都係不可或缺嘅知識，YouTube會成為你嘅良師。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n=====================================<br />\n以下開放討論~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae0cb1af5ba0f23c99c8612e10f148e1c0fb0f3","tid":33705,"uid":60735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T04:06:07.000Z","msg":"膠問<br />\n如果新手由0開始 應該點樣開始學 同埋有咩軟件有幫助<br />\n好有興趣 但唔知點入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"496adcc23e17493fa94e00d40412736b72b257ce","tid":33705,"uid":5751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T04:16:28.000Z","msg":"我係亞洲zedd"},{"pid":"cd31cebf2332b3b9ef889a6f7784938bd1a471ab","tid":33705,"uid":34626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T11:33:39.000Z","msg":"冇音樂底整唔整倒"},{"pid":"52297a98b1f7c7d2001997c1ea01119ddb403ae2","tid":33705,"uid":63158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:14:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>膠問<br />\n如果新手由0開始 應該點樣開始學 同埋有咩軟件有幫助<br />\n好有興趣 但唔知點入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nDownload唔同DAW(Digital Audio Workstation)嘅免費版，用MIDI整啲音出嚟玩下先。<br />\n<br />\n睇YouTube教學，keyword:How to make electronic music. 例如<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hynl84dyDq4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dhynl84dyDq4&d=JLAdynOSApH72bnt5W8YUH8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=bf221a6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hynl84dyDq4</a>由零開始到完成一首歌，從中可以學到好多嘢。<br />\n<br />\n巴打加油，唔需要心急，起碼浸幾年先會有啲成績。Alan Walker話過自己花咗一年時間完全專注睇YouTube片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9ef0cec924c43d2af10d73b77c0c190436f4e3","tid":33705,"uid":63158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係亞洲zedd</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aca2a28c4533a45fdd246db930ae4f5bb5aefb1","tid":33705,"uid":10774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:17:03.000Z","msg":"香港玩音樂無錢途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9273e4ba0301e6abf51c569bcc0f951fc3b4afd1","tid":33705,"uid":63158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:18:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇音樂底整唔整倒</blockquote><br />\n好少有咁嘅案例，唔係唔得，但冇音樂底就唔識寫chord, melody等等。我覺得音樂基礎佔60%入場門檻。除非你係天才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5041e33040fa3004d462a445a3c5c857f0d73815","tid":33705,"uid":60207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:22:20.000Z","msg":"終於有EDM Produce交流Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打你平時整EDM個步驟係咩？ 整左個Chord，Melody 再整Intro？ <br />\n<br />\n利申 Fl Studio 12用家 最鐘意Trap同埋Future House Progressive House"},{"pid":"f4ab7ef8b90bd531446eee22fa9787e7db62024f","tid":33705,"uid":60207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:22:55.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"9c35292ca4cd5d2a64015bd30d9711e704afe71e","tid":33705,"uid":63158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:27:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港玩音樂無錢途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />越諗越灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我極愛音樂，冇諗過放棄。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打是咪同道之士?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76db34935128517df944771df80d79f49b865ba7","tid":33705,"uid":63158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:33:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>終於有EDM Produce交流Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打你平時整EDM個步驟係咩？ 整左個Chord，Melody 再整Intro？ <br />\n<br />\n利申 Fl Studio 12用家 最鐘意Trap同埋Future House Progressive House</blockquote><br />\n我會喺Breakdown或Verse開始，因為嗰度係首歌嘅靈魂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b1b31a34d50f1b8476e6f1f1997b158d761898","tid":33705,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:38:25.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"9abbb6ce6f4fca3b166f25a5982052724f59dc82","tid":33705,"uid":60207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:38:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>終於有EDM Produce交流Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打你平時整EDM個步驟係咩？ 整左個Chord，Melody 再整Intro？ <br />\n<br />\n利申 Fl Studio 12用家 最鐘意Trap同埋Future House Progressive House</blockquote><br />\n我會喺Breakdown或Verse開始，因為嗰度係首歌嘅靈魂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知點解成日 整好Chord 整好Melody 反而諗唔到好既Intro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到成日都有堆Chord Melody廢置咗係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d833e3232f0c3640ff302a98b8357332fec97734","tid":33705,"uid":63158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:39:25.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"a2eb337db35833894134d9ac094ac99b281cc01d","tid":33705,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:40:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名</blockquote><br />\n自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28dc1da10a710f3a6d680dea687c2ceeae34045","tid":33705,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:42:35.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"632cb16a8baafb737fa91234c3900f3f8d486542","tid":33705,"uid":63158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:48:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>終於有EDM Produce交流Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打你平時整EDM個步驟係咩？ 整左個Chord，Melody 再整Intro？ <br />\n<br />\n利申 Fl Studio 12用家 最鐘意Trap同埋Future House Progressive House</blockquote><br />\n我會喺Breakdown或Verse開始，因為嗰度係首歌嘅靈魂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知點解成日 整好Chord 整好Melody 反而諗唔到好既Intro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到成日都有堆Chord Melody廢置咗係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都經歷過呢個階段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nintro唔需要複雜，佢嘅作用係醞釀成首歌嘅脈絡精髓。<br />\n<br />\nambience同drum sample風格要一致，用lowpass filter凝聚張力，加上transistion fx(noise&amp;riser)過渡去verse，intro就搞掂了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb0e51c784832efaa3c625107d52c2fccf5994ca","tid":33705,"uid":16884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:54:09.000Z","msg":"幫推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n近排我買左部打碟機，仲學緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴絲打開碟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56aec5372a80ad24d2c1f50730aad023ce934e15","tid":33705,"uid":16884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:58:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做咗CD ROM好耐，特此發文慶祝連登啟業！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我聽開Avicii, Alesso, Flume, Martin Garrix, Marshmello, Galantis, Porter Robinson, Madeon, Oliver Heldens, KSHMR, Zedd 等等大路製作人。<br />\n<br />\n比較小眾嘅有<span style=\"color: gold;\">Grey, <span style=\"color: red;\">Kap Slap</span>, Justin Caruso.</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (高度推薦)<br />\n<br />\n喜愛類型: Big Room, Dubstep, Melodic Progressive House, Future House, Futurebass, Melbourne Bounce, Chill.<br />\n<br />\n=====================================<br />\n<br />\nMusic Production方面，玩咗幾年，未有起色，不過基本功尚足。<br />\n用過Ableton Live, 依家係FL Studio忠粉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSamples儲埋成107GB, 不過最常用嘅有12.7GB. KSHMR Sounds, Cymatics, Vengeance House, 都係高質samples.<br />\n<br />\nSynth/Sound Plugin: Sylenth1, Massive, Serum, Spire, Addictive Keys, Kontakt 5.<br />\n<br />\nFX Plugin: Fabfilters, Valhalla DSP, Dimension Expander, OTT, Camel Crusher. Waves Complete Bundle. <br />\n<br />\n以上所提及嘅，夠你做Avicii, Martin Garrix嗰啲架啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n=====================================<br />\n<br />\nEssential Knowledge:<br />\nSound Design, Layering, Mixing(EQ, Pan), Automation, Compression, Arrangement.<br />\n<br />\n呢啲都係不可或缺嘅知識，YouTube會成為你嘅良師。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n=====================================<br />\n以下開放討論~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFelt this good 唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3ddb9c4841de112ba07b3cbcdd50d146659c76","tid":33705,"uid":60207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:06:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>終於有EDM Produce交流Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打你平時整EDM個步驟係咩？ 整左個Chord，Melody 再整Intro？ <br />\n<br />\n利申 Fl Studio 12用家 最鐘意Trap同埋Future House Progressive House</blockquote><br />\n我會喺Breakdown或Verse開始，因為嗰度係首歌嘅靈魂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知點解成日 整好Chord 整好Melody 反而諗唔到好既Intro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到成日都有堆Chord Melody廢置咗係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都經歷過呢個階段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nintro唔需要複雜，佢嘅作用係醞釀成首歌嘅脈絡精髓。<br />\n<br />\nambience同drum sample風格要一致，用lowpass filter凝聚張力，加上transistion fx(noise&amp;riser)過渡去verse，intro就搞掂了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我仲係新手階段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前係整開Launchpad Project 到前一排開始想自己整埋歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"312b1f978bde5d48d813587a34628af5698702dc","tid":33705,"uid":16884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:55:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知點解成日 整好Chord 整好Melody 反而諗唔到好既Intro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到成日都有堆Chord Melody廢置咗係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都經歷過呢個階段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nintro唔需要複雜，佢嘅作用係醞釀成首歌嘅脈絡精髓。<br />\n<br />\nambience同drum sample風格要一致，用lowpass filter凝聚張力，加上transistion fx(noise&amp;amp;riser)過渡去verse，intro就搞掂了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我仲係新手階段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前係整開Launchpad Project 到前一排開始想自己整埋歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想學launchpad，巴打玩launchpad洗唔洗音樂底？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c95693befba2e19ab0aef4c83f18693bf0b9e9f0","tid":33705,"uid":56388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:07:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>終於有EDM Produce交流Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打你平時整EDM個步驟係咩？ 整左個Chord，Melody 再整Intro？ <br />\n<br />\n利申 Fl Studio 12用家 最鐘意Trap同埋Future House Progressive House</blockquote><br />\n（搭嘴）<br />\n整Hardstyle整個Kick整成個月（都整唔好）<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e477a532de84a1d02cf9c3b94935019efd5ce28d","tid":33705,"uid":37329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:09:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"389f4df96e302e959c640cfe20777002c43288af","tid":33705,"uid":44804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:16:35.000Z","msg":"留個靚名<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803d24e46440