1989fca9ba458","tid":33705,"uid":63158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:16:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打點開始學? 冇音樂底可以點補 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1.睇好多YouTube教學，日月累積；<br />\n2.用心研究商業級嘅歌，知己知彼；<br />\n3.投放時間自己試吓整歌。<br />\n<br />\n冇音樂底相對難開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理解基本樂理先(interval, scale chord)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ea5e74654831f58094bdb77bfb5d4cc426ce40","tid":33705,"uid":63158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:17:32.000Z","msg":"＃1《器材篇》<br />\n<br />\n好多人以為整音樂門檻高，要買好多器材。其實，一部電腦就夠。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好俾商家迷惑，好多嘢都係冇需要。(Skrillex用laptop喇叭整歌架)<br />\n<br />\n不過，以下幾樣，個人認為值得入手。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一，Midi keyboard。好多時彈琴嘅手感唔係用電腦做到，有鋼琴底的，建議買個49鍵 keyboard,會順手好多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n二，純淨音色嘅耳機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。推薦Audio Technica M50x 同埋 Beyerdynamics 嘅DT Series. 做歌講求準確聲音傳遞。What you hear is what you get. Beats嘅音染只會壞事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n三，聲卡/DAC/Audio Interface。普遍Motherboard對音質要求唔高，會有底噪，或延遲等問題。入手interface係不二之選。<br />\n<br />\n四，電競滑鼠。好多粒自訂制，用嚟做shortcut一流，整歌效率蒸蒸日上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ee8f0399b2eb5f91dc84e41649dc44891d845b","tid":33705,"uid":60207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:30:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>＃1《器材篇》<br />\n<br />\n好多人以為整音樂門檻高，要買好多器材。其實，一部電腦就夠。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好俾商家迷惑，好多嘢都係冇需要。(Skrillex用laptop喇叭整歌架)<br />\n<br />\n不過，以下幾樣，個人認為值得入手。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一，Midi k