ce。普遍Motherboard對音質要求唔高，會有底噪，或延遲等問題。入手interface係不二之選。<br />\n<br />\n四，電競滑鼠。好多粒自訂制，用嚟做shortcut一流，整歌效率蒸蒸日上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諗緊學唔學基本既鋼琴 之後用嚟玩電子琴攞靈感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鋼琴知識一定會幫到好多，搵chord諗melody都得心應手。雖然自己受正統鋼琴教育，但我覺得鋼琴可以自學。巴打加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a1adcc0ac312a93fee37271890f379ee0164561","tid":33705,"uid":16884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T17:59:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>＃1《器材篇》<br />\n<br />\n好多人以為整音樂門檻高，要買好多器材。其實，一部電腦就夠。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好俾商家迷惑，好多嘢都係冇需要。(Skrillex用laptop喇叭整歌架)<br />\n<br />\n不過，以下幾樣，個人認為值得入手。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一，Midi keyboard。好多時彈琴嘅手感唔係用電腦做到，有鋼琴底的，建議買個49鍵 keyboard,會順手好多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n二，純淨音色嘅耳機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。推薦Audio Technica M50x 同埋 Beyerdynamics 嘅DT Series. 做歌講求準確聲音傳遞。What you hear is what you get. Beats嘅音染只會壞事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n三，聲卡/DAC/Audio Interface。普遍Motherboard對音質要求唔高，會有底噪，或延遲等問題。入手interface係不二之選。<br />\n<br />\n四，電競滑鼠。好多粒自訂制，用嚟做shortcut一流，整歌效率蒸蒸日上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打 <br />\n<br />\n我都係諗住自學琴先，順便攞下靈感"},{"pid":"0cd1ce70d7b1183dda9827bb2cbf81da49dd73aa","tid":33705,"uid":52254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:34:37.000Z","msg":"想學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829b25d1463940a28784745664f8bf860b5f42f4","tid":33705,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,